{"tid":2485770,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有得買青梅啦，可以整梅酒 / 青梅糖漿","createTime":"2021-04-12T12:06:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T04:19:51.000Z","uid":3290,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e2bc1113b0b1e46b48a78ee81a29ba9c0c324dc6","tid":2485770,"uid":3290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T12:06:42.000Z","msg":"老母早兩日係街市買咗啲梅返黎整<br />\n叫佢幫手買啲<br />\n點知老豆買咗七磅返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQooAdtNZ7TB6iYtWfk47ec7AYXbQnpjjRKhfcDPpjkpk?filename=cDhGncd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcDhGncd.jpg&h=f77ad46e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">日本梅請等到五月，而家個啲係支那梅</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n係之前啲Post抄返黎：<br />\n1. 洗乾淨 揀好梅<br />\n2. 用牙簽整走個叮 用酒洗樽同梅<br />\n3. 吹乾<br />\n4, 自行決定用唔用叉吉梅身<br />\n5. 糖+梅+酒入去封好<br />\n用咩酒都得<br />\n只要&gt;25%先可以殺到菌<br />\n<br />\n黃店暫時揾到Mr. Fresh Fruit, Get Fresh O2O, 華叔生果檔, Let's Jam<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>舊Posts</ins><br />\n<span class=\"small\">又差唔多時候浸梅酒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2011377\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2011377</a><br />\n<br />\n青梅有得賣了，係時候浸梅酒！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/619189\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/619189</a></span>"},{"pid":"9bf062a2c466db806a2a2f0b0ecfce737b1ab952","tid":2485770,"uid":298104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T13:27:42.000Z","msg":"今年未決定整唔整梅酒，上年仲有樽未開<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n留名睇大家用咩梅"},{"pid":"da589f93ee51d186d10b7ac384aac77cf5f308f4","tid":2485770,"uid":3290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bf062a2c466db806a2a2f0b0ecfce737b1ab952","tid":2485770,"uid":298104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T13:27:42.000Z","msg":"今年未決定整唔整梅酒，上年仲有樽未開<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n留名睇大家用咩梅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-1