13T23:51:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 浸一年威都咁嘅色啦<br />\n浸兩年再深色啲有咩出奇<br />\n<br />\n同埋，你洗咩腳可以咁黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXZvx5PF377gwL9X7Jtz8CudXHTdKmHV6vmsSBWBo1uzd?filename=F3VEkS0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF3VEkS0.jpg&h=c53a1276&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"768447421305dfd0fb40d035abc489aa54bfa281","tid":2485770,"uid":3290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T05:07:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"786864408eb0d3986bcf2c39ab82d024408cc565","tid":2485770,"uid":8401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"768447421305dfd0fb40d035abc489aa54bfa281","tid":2485770,"uid":3290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T05:07:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:37:30.000Z","msg":"可唔可以分享下你上年個d 浸成點"},{"pid":"25fdae1f4871816d1de8fce55cff9091e06679be","tid":2485770,"uid":3290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"786864408eb0d3986bcf2c39ab82d024408cc565","tid":2485770,"uid":8401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"768447421305dfd0fb40d035abc489aa54bfa281","tid":2485770,"uid":3290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T05:07:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:37:30.000Z","msg":"可唔可以分享下你上年個d 浸成點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T00:52:01.000Z","msg":"好呀..........呢個係上年個樽，用返再上年剩低嘅Famous Grouse<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再加三溫糖＋和歌山梅（係Donki買）<br />\n六月先浸，八月定九月試過味，無之前個年咁好味<br />\n我估係未浸到出哂味掛<br />\n過兩日會再試吓<br />\n<br />\n我見台灣啲Blogger用唔同嘅糖去做配搭，有心思嘅可以好似佢哋咁玩吓<br />\n最好寫返低個配搭，覺得好味第二年可以再浸過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSEjpexH7N2XuNJdUptQLP1xLDUEjorApFX2XHMbEnsrP?filename=KO6s944.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKO6s944.jpg&h=bbaafee7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db14fc27ccdc77a3c474b2ec1e499cb7969b15fd","tid":2485770,"uid":38033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T01:03:08.000Z","msg":"上年浸左1set (1.8L 燒灼，1Kg 南高，3盒太古冰糖），對我黎講就甜到瀨屎，但係係隊淋條女既神器<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年諗住試下紫gay/紫南高，但係似乎未有一間放風入貴梅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw 請教樓主點浸梅汁？<br />\n 係咪梅同糖1：1塞入樽就得？連蜜糖/水咩都唔駛？"},{"pid":"81adc82541ed604f725c90cb77ad5a2d8f5c8a46","tid":2485770,"uid":3290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db14fc27ccdc77a3c474b2ec1e499cb7969b15fd","tid":2485770,"uid":38033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T01:03:08.000Z","msg":"上年浸左1set (1.8L 燒灼，1Kg 南高，3盒太古冰糖），對我黎講就甜到瀨屎，但係係隊淋條女既神器<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年諗住試下紫gay/紫南高，但係似乎未有一間放風入貴梅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw 請教樓主點浸梅汁？<br />\n 係咪梅同糖1：1塞入樽就得？連蜜糖/水咩都唔駛？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:16:03.000Z","msg":"太甜就沖梳打水，下次整個陣落少啲糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係呀，整糖漿就咁梅同糖就得架啦<br />\n啲梅過咗幾日就會縮得好勁，面又會有少少泡，係正常嘅<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/jrseface/1465058069-3011664200_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fjrseface%2F1465058069-3011664200_n.jpg&h=e267948a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://jrseface.pixnet.net/blog/post/43838347-%E5%A4%8F%E6%97%A5%E9%A3%B2%E5%93%81~%E6%A2%85%E5%AD%90%E7%B3%96%E6%BC%BF?pixfrom=related\" dat